## 2. Color Palette & Roles

### Primary
- **[Brand Color]** (`#hex`): Primary brand color, CTA backgrounds, interactive highlights
- **[Heading Color]** (`#hex`): Primary heading text — [warm/cold/neutral character]
- **[Background]** (`#hex`): Page background, primary canvas

### Secondary & Accent
- **[Accent]** (`#hex`): Secondary accent for decorative elements, icons
- **[Dark Section]** (`#hex`): Immersive dark sections, footer

### Interactive
- **[CTA Color]** (`#hex`): Primary link color, active states
- **[Hover]** (`#hex`): Hover state for primary elements
- **[Focus Ring]** (`#hex`): Keyboard focus indicator

### Text Scale
- **[Primary Text]** (`#hex`): Headings, strong labels
- **[Body Text]** (`#hex`): Secondary text, descriptions, captions
- **[Label]** (`#hex`): Form labels, metadata
- **[Disabled]** (`rgba(...)`): Disabled/muted text

### Surface & Borders
- **[Surface]** (`#hex`): Cards, elevated containers
- **[Border Default]** (`#hex`): Standard card/divider borders
- **[Border Active]** (`#hex`): Active/selected state borders

### Semantic
- **[Success]** (`#hex`): Success indicators, positive states
- **[Warning]** (`#hex`): Warning states, caution
- **[Error]** (`#hex`): Error states, destructive actions

### Shadow Colors
- **[Primary Shadow]** (`rgba(...)`): Main shadow color — [describe tinting philosophy]
- **[Ambient Shadow]** (`rgba(...)`): Soft ambient lift

### Gradient System
- [Brand Gradient]: `#fromHex` to `#toHex` — [where/how used: hero decorations, backgrounds]
- [Note if brand avoids gradients: "Flat color only — no UI gradients"]

## 3. Typography Rules

