| Display Hero | [font] | [N]px | [N] | [N] | -[N]px | [ss01] | [usage context] |
| Display Large | [font] | [N]px | [N] | [N] | -[N]px | [ss01] | [usage context] |
| Section Heading | [font] | [N]px | [N] | [N] | -[N]px | [ss01] | [usage context] |
| Sub-heading | [font] | [N]px | [N] | [N] | -[N]px | [ss01] | [usage context] |
| Body Large | [font] | [N]px | [N] | [N] | normal | [ss01] | [usage context] |
| Body | [font] | [N]px | [N] | [N] | normal | [ss01] | [usage context] |
| Button | [font] | [N]px | [N] | [N] | normal | [ss01] | [usage context] |
| Caption | [font] | [N]px | [N] | [N] | normal | [ss01] | [usage context] |
| Disclaimer | [font] | [N]px | [N] | [N] | normal | | [smallest text] |

