## 4. Component Stylings

### Buttons

**Primary**
- Background: `#hex`
- Text: `#hex`
- Padding: [N]px [N]px
- Radius: [N]px
- Font: [N]px [font] weight [N], `"ss01"`
- Hover: `#hoverHex` background
- Use: Primary CTA ("Get started", "Sign up")

**Ghost / Outlined**
- Background: transparent
- Text: `#hex`
- Padding: [N]px [N]px
- Radius: [N]px
- Border: `1px solid #hex`
- Hover: background shifts to `rgba(...)`
- Use: Secondary actions

**Tertiary / Text**
- Background: transparent
- Text: `#hex`
- Padding: [N]px [N]px
- Radius: [N]px
- Hover: underline or subtle background
- Use: Low-emphasis actions, links

**Destructive** (if applicable)
- Background: `#errorHex`
- Text: `#hex`
- Radius: [N]px
- Use: Delete, remove, cancel

### Cards & Containers
- Background: `#hex`
- Border: `1px solid #hex`
- Radius: [N]px (tight), [N]px (standard), [N]px (featured)
- Shadow: `[full CSS box-shadow values]`
- Padding: [N]px
- Hover: shadow intensifies / border color change / slight lift

### Badges / Tags / Pills

**[Default Badge]**
- Background: `#hex` or `rgba(...)`
- Text: `#hex`
- Padding: [N]px [N]px
- Radius: [N]px
- Font: [N]px weight [N]

### Inputs & Forms
- Border: `1px solid #hex`
- Radius: [N]px
- Height: [N]px
- Focus: `1px solid #focusHex` or focus ring
- Label: `#hex`, [N]px [font]
- Text: `#hex`
- Placeholder: `#hex`
- Background: `#hex`

### Navigation
- Height: [N]px
- Background: `#hex` [sticky with blur backdrop?]
- Links: [font] [N]px weight [N], `#hex` text
- Active indicator: [underline | background | bold | dot]
- CTA: [describe nav CTA button]
- Mobile: [hamburger? slide-out? bottom bar?]

### Image Treatment
- [Border radius on images: 0px / product images, [N]px editorial]
- [Aspect ratio guidelines]
- [Overlay/scrim approach for text on images]

