## 6. Depth & Elevation

| Level | Treatment | Use |
|-------|-----------|-----|
| Flat (Level 0) | No shadow | Page background, inline text |
| Ambient (Level 1) | `[shadow values]` | Subtle card lift, hover hints |
| Standard (Level 2) | `[shadow values]` | Standard cards, content panels |
| Elevated (Level 3) | `[multi-layer shadow values]` | Featured cards, dropdowns |
| Floating (Level 4) | `[shadow values]` | Modals, floating panels |

**Shadow Philosophy**: [How depth works in this brand. Blue-tinted shadows? Luminance stacking for dark themes? Multi-layer parallax? Borders instead of shadows?]

