- "Design a card: [bg] background, 1px solid #hex border, [N]px radius. Shadow: [values]. Title at [N]px weight [N], color #hex, '[tag]'. Body at [N]px, #hex."
- "Build a badge: [bg] background, #hex text, [N]px radius, [N]px [N]px padding, [N]px weight [N]."
- "Create navigation: [bg] sticky header. [font] [N]px weight [N] for links, #hex text, '[tag]'. [Primary] CTA right-aligned."

### Iteration Guide
1. Always enable `font-feature-settings: "[tags]"` on [font] text — brand typographic DNA
2. Weight [N] is the default; use [N] only for [context]
3. Shadow formula: [describe multi-layer approach]
4. Heading color is `#hex`, body is `#hex`, labels are `#hex`
5. Border-radius stays in [N]-[N]px range — [reasoning]
6. Spacing snaps to the scale: [list key values]
7. Dark sections use `#hex` — not black, not gray, branded
